title: Is a stylish catio possible? (building a patio for our cat)
author: Evan and Katelyn
description:
We’re making a bigger, better, and much improved catio (cat patio) for our Supurrvisor! Thanks to our sponsor Squarespace, go to https://www.squarespace.com/evanandkatelyn for 10% off your first purchase. Check out the tools / materials we used below! 👇

🙏 Other sponsors:
Rockler: Want the largest selection of woodworking tools? Rockler has you covered. Check out what we used in today’s video below and browse their selection here: https://bit.ly/EK-Rockler 

Check out the Patreon Aftershow for:
- Seeing our first prototype
- Did we seem stressed in this video?
- Design changes we ALMOST did
- The struggle of making woodworking entertaining
- Why we put off this video for so long
- Would we change anything? 
If you're a Patron already, watch it here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/59168509
Not a Patron yet? Join here: https://www.patreon.com/evanandkatelyn

Check out the 3d model:  https://evanandkatelyn.com/2021/11/modern-catio-a-patio-for-our-cat/
